dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Cuddy Valley quadrangle, Ventura & Kern Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Cuddy Valley, CA 1995, NIMA 2153 I SE -- Series V895." "First printing, March 2006." "Arthur G. Sylvester Honorary Map." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
